---
source: starstream-compiler/src/typecheck/tests.rs
description: "Source:\n\nfn test() {\n    let x = Result::Err(false);\n}\n"
---
T-Fn: test => ()
  T-Let: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ let x = Result::Err(false); ⇒ Result
    T-Call: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ Result::Err(false) ⇒ Result
      T-Var: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ Result::Err ⇒ fn(t4) -> Result [1]
      T-Bool: {test: fn() -> () [test]} ⊢ false ⇒ bool
      Unify-Var: bool ~ t4 => {bool/t4}
